Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe you're\Nletting me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As your pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor's a\Nfather! I'm an aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first friendship\Nlesson is going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,reuniting with Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes, that's me. Yep.\NHa ha. Important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby is an alicorn!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she could be a\Nsuper strong flyer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and have crazy baby magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Heart, the Crystal\NEmpire is about to be buried
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,under a mountain\Nof ice and snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NEat all muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, not only can\Nwe not take part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in a fabulous,\Nancient ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're also about\Nto be frozen solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Crystal Heart's\Nmagical protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire city is about to\Nbecome a winter wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about\Nwhen King Sombra
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ruled the\NCrystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Crystal\NHeart was missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The city wasn't\Ncovered in snow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heart wasn't missing.\NIt was still in the Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra had\Njust hidden it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid Twilight\Nis correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And the storm clouds\Nare already forming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can totally fly up there\Nand bust those puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't advise it,\NRainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those storm clouds are not\Nlike the ones you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This far north, the weather\Nhas a will of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it will\Nonly grow stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,enveloping everything\Nin its path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the\NCrystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And us along with it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Princess Twilight\Nis keen on the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rekindling our friendship,\Nbut it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how anything on\Nthat list is going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? It's not\Nlike there's some spell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that would magically compel us\Nto pick up where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually, there's several.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistmane's Material Amity,\NRockhoof's Rapport,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Flashprance's Fellowship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I get the\Nfeeling the Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't looking for a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and if all else\Nfails, ask them to share
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,an embarrassing moment\Nfrom their past,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe even something\Nthey regret."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't see how\Nthat would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. We should just\Nget out of your mane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious this isn't\Ngoing how Twilight hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm sure you have plenty\Nof important work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh. Right. Yes.\NNo rest for the wizardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a spell that can\Nrestore the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't something\Nthat either of us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The library here at the\NCastle is nearly as extensive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as the one in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance we\Ncan find something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hold off the storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for a time, but even our\Nmagic will eventually succumb
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to the power of\Nthe Frozen North.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do what we can,\Nbut you must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long it will\Ntake to find the right spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but you should probably\Ntell the crowd outside
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to get somewhere warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And try not to mention\Nthe Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to start a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!\NCome on, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need\Nall of your help;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the Crystal library\Nis enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on us, Twiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Spike, looks like my\Nbiggest fears came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised\Nif Twilight decides
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to give up on me entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who said all\Nwe needed was this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the list, Spike.\NOr you. Or Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one Sunburst doesn't\Nwant to be friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember him saying\Nhe didn't want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Twilight obviously thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you're worth being\Nfriends with and I do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw thanks, Spike. At\Nleast I have two friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,even if one of them\Nhas dragon breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's not dragon\Nbreath. It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought the Crystal\NHeart was supposed to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the cold weather out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, unless something's\Nhappened! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just saying that it\Nmight not be the best idea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I camped out all\Nnight for this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not about to\Njust give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the view is just as good\Na little further back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like inside your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystalling ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of our most\Nsacred traditions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and when that foal is held\Nbefore the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to be as close to\Nthe action as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's gonna\Nbe a Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is the\Nbaby's an alicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and her magic's plum crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so you might not want to\Nbe that close after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby alicorn? Wow. I\Ncan't wait to see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those little wings\Nare probably so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I am 100% sure the\NCrystalling isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No Crystalling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are they\Nstarting a fireworks show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,WOO-HOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Young filly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to your Auntie Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridlebuck's Boat Chants,\NHayhoof's Intonements,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystic Maps and Mazes.\NAnything up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. I'm not even sure\Nhow these are organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Geeeeya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor, I thought you\Nwere taking care of the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the long or\Nthe short version?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Short?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's an alicorn and\Nshe accidentally destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the Crystal Heart so Twilight\Nand Cadance are looking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for a spell to put\Nit back together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and save the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from turning into a giant\Nwasteland of ice and snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this? Trotter's\NTome of Reliquary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spell of Relic Reconstitution!\NI can't believe we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Without this, I don't\Nknow what we'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell was the only thing\Nwe found in the whole library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that was even close\Nto what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry,\NTwilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us were\Nexpecting any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can\Nremember the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I only read it through once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if anypony can\Nexactly remember something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,she read for the first\Ntime two minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try, but I'm not\Nsure how long it'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is quickly an option?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should evacuate\Nthe city just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to lead everypony\Nto the train station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,before the tracks freeze over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We will. But between\Nyou and Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll\Nremember the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hope this spell\Nis the one we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. I'm just\Nsorry about your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst and I don't have\Nanything in common anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big important wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm relearning everything\NI ever thought I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst? I don't\Nrecognize the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but if he's an\Nimportant wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you should\Nbring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll know what to\Ndo if the spell fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You better go with her, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst! Haven't\Nyou looked outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow? That's not right.\NThe Crystal Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...is gone. The baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor and Cadance's\Nbaby. It's an alicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! And her magic\Nis a little berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and, well, I guess she\Ndestroyed the Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Twilight thinks\Nshe can fix it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and Princess Cadance\Nthought you could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're an important\Nwizard in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It just makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'd like to\Nhelp. I-I really would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just have so much, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,important wizard work\Nto do around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I mention this was\Na Royal Crystalling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Crystaller holds\Nthe young one aloft,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the Empire will\Nshare their joy and light
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Crystal Heart\Nwill beat stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,than it ever has before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a moving ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think\Nit's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's freezing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen snow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance has decided\Nto evacuate the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Crystalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we'll\Never have another
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystalling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart is shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we've been\Ntrying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst, I know you're busy,\Nbut did you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard you,\Nbut-but like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're an important\Nwizard the work just piles up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Starlight, I\Nwant to help, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't. I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixing an ancient relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't even come close to\Ndoing something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were\Nan important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were wrong! OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an important wizard!\NI'm not even a wizard at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard for\Nyou to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but not all of us end\Nup achieving greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why wouldn't\NI understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're the protégé of\Nthe Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she picks\Njust anypony for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, she's more of\Na student than a protégé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I'm sorry I'm not\Nthe big, important wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you were expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst! I don't care if\Nyou're a wizard or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just surprised. You always\Nknew so much about magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at all these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, reading\Nabout magic is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't know what it\Nwas like at Magic School,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to know so much and not\Nbe able to do any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't know what it\Nwas like to be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then getting so bitter\Nthat you steal the cutie marks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from an entire village\Nand then get defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,by Twilight and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you travel through\Ntime to get back at them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but they beat you again and\Nteach you about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're so terrified ponies\Nwill find out what you did
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't make any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really\Ntravel through time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you\Nhe'd be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we lost touch.\NMaybe if I had reached out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have helped\Nme at Magic School
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could have\Nhelped you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not become totally evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say\NI know what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to have something you're\Nnot exactly proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed up thinking\NI was some big wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I should\Nhave told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. At least\Nwe worked it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Twilight\Nwould be proud of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ever want\Nto tell her about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we should probably leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you,\Nthey're evacuating the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get to\Nthe train station,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you've got a spell here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that will drive back\Nthe Frozen North
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and fix the Crystal Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so the baby can have\Nher Crystalling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystalling. Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Push them back, my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit\Nfurther, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The station's just ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I think that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks right to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's only\None way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell failed. I don't\Nknow what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An old student of\Nmine believes he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby did this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried putting it\Nback together with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Spell of Relic\NReconstitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart's been\Naround for millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Restoring a relic like this is\Nmagic way beyond one spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd need to combine\Nit with something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,something unique to\Nthe relic itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,something that strengthens it\Nand provides it with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Combining that spell\Nwith the light and love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of everypony gathered for the\Nceremony, together with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Somnambula's Weather Abjuration
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to clear away the snow and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A little Fledgling's\NForbearance for the parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That should curb the little\None's power fluctuations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight said you\Nwere a powerful wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm no wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But he studied magic\Nhis whole life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And since no pony\Nhas any better ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what do we have to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I had planned on asking\NTwilight to be our Crystaller,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but since it seems\Nlike she'll be busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens, may I present\Nthe newest member
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's just so moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Best. Crystalling. Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Pony who isn't great at\Nmagic, you did pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see\Nyou've found a way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to share your unique\Ngift, Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be more of a\Nwizard than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You would not believe\Nthe crazy weather
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that delayed our train!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was all worth it to see\Nthis peaceful little angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww so sweet, come\Nto your grandmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Peaceful now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that spell\Nreally did the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Sunburst\Nto thank for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he takes his role\Nas Crystaller seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me the baby\Nwill need a pony like him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to look to for magical advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadence, darling,\Naren't we going to name
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the poor little dear or\Nare we going to spend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire visit just\Ncalling her "the baby?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We were thinking, Flurry Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to remember\Nthe occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh goodness! How\Ncould anypony forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you're\Nthe Crystal Empire's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,big, important wizard,\Nwhether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll have\Ntime for any wizarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Crystaller now.\NThat's a big responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of\Nanypony more qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just promise you'll\Nstay in touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever lose touch\Nwith my oldest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have a lot to\Nlearn about being a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYour lesson went perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and Sunburst\Ngot over their past
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and rekindled their friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot happened; I\Njust wish I could have given
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,my pupil the attention\Nshe deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know she needed to\Nbe put on the right path,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but giving her the space\Nto make her own decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,worked pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how\NCelestia taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I never thought\Nabout it, but I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're a better\Nteacher than you thought.
